PID: http://data.europa.eu/89h/a0df7a6f-49de-46ea-9bde-563437a6e2ba, doi:10.2905/A0DF7A6F-49DE-46EA-9BDE-563437A6E2BA

All the percentages for electoral demographics are calculated by Tindak Malaysia using publicly available Elections Lab data. There is no official ethnic demographic data. Sum of percentages for electoral demographics may not attain exact 100% but the variation is kept less than 2%. Elections Lab data has margin of error of +/-5%. Spelling for parliamentary seat of Alor Setar was corrected on 17/2/2024. TindakMalaysia Network Services PLT is not responsible for any errors or ommissions arising from the original data or its derivatives
